                    <span>I know I rated this picture just one star, but I just wanted to be next to those who rated it the same. Ken Burns is a master story teller. If you want "just the facts" go to the library. I don't know why he catches flack from some people, but I guess it's their lose. It's hard to believe you could be so wrapped up in a story about any historical figure. I only wish my teachers and proffesors could have kept me this intrested. Amazing.</span>
                  
                    <div class="CustomerReviewSummary">yet another Ken Burns ode to himself</div>
                    <div>
                      <span class="ItemCaption">Rating: </span>
